hopobject.body: Have you got any ? how much does 8fit app cost --3B Alex Rodriguez (left hip surgery in January 2013) went on the 60-day disabled list Feb. 13. He began a rehab assignment with Class A Charleston on July 2, then moved his rehab to Class A Tampa on July 5. He is expected to take the full 20 days before returning. He was sent on a rehab assignment to Trenton on July 15 and then Scranton/Wilkes-Barre July 18. He was supposed to make his 2013 debut in Texas on July 22, but an MRI on an injured quad July 21 showed a Grade 1 strain. He's being sent back to the team's complex in Tampa for rest and treatment. He was returned from his rehab 20-day rehab assignment, but remains on the disabled list.
